\u003cp data-pid=\"4sBTJ1IP\"\u003e16.马善被人骑人善被人欺\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"9sdvtTYX\"\u003e17.为什么投资比创业还要难?\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"fdEApUoo\"\u003e18.所有的成功都是反人性的\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"GWBHzC3t\"\u003e19.大众传媒都是魅众的\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"9C9Cd3lM\"\u003e20.低标准不可能出现高成绩\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"I5S8V1KD\"\u003e21.教育的目的不是为了培养成功者的\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"ED4_R_my\"\u003e22.商人重利轻离别\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"5Z7ZitpI\"\u003e下载地址：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//mp.weixin.qq.com/s/XWkkZbwbePMfgUhmneM4iQ\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"invisible\"\u003ehttps://\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"visible\"\u003emp.weixin.qq.com/s/XWkk\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"invisible\"\u003eZbwbePMfgUhmneM4iQ\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"ellipsis\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","is_labeled":false,"visited_count":12,"thumbnails":["https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-1864fceb7abc7e251aeea022db4201e7.jpg?source=7e7ef6e2\u0026needBackground=1"],"favorite_count":0,"article_type":"normal","is_navigator":false,"navigator_vote":false,"vote_next_step":"vote"},"brief":"{\"source\": \"TS\", \"type\": \"article\", \"id\": 1933532820766187796}","attached_info":"","action_card":false},{"id":"119_1753854192.992","type":"feed","offset":119,"verb":"TOPIC_ACKNOWLEDGED_ANSWER","created_time":1753854192,"updated_time":1753854192,"target":{"id":"3519128610","type":"answer","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/answers/3519128610","author":{"id":"0af39908632189078bc780bfa425fdbc","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/people/0af39908632189078bc780bfa425fdbc","user_type":"people","url_token":"jia-ran-ran-92","name":"贾然然","headline":"网站的站长","avatar_url":"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-26af4c6d028be0ba7eb8216df5aed008_l.